follow these steps:
https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/configuration/wireless/access-point-routed.md

after that install 
nginx for forwarding 
https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/remote-access/web-server/nginx.md

setup nginx 
////
create new file 
sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/1pekway

server {
listen 80;
server_name pkw.wlan ;

location / {
proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:1880/ui/;
}
}


restart nginx
sudo systemctl restart nginx


we have changed gt.wlan to pekaway.wlan, if you are connect you can reach the dashboard there. 


wifikey: pekawayYES
ssid:pekwaDIYcontrol











